value.question: What are the names and email addresses of all customers?
value.sql_query: SELECT FirstName, LastName, EmailAddress FROM SalesLT.Customer;

value.question: How many products are currently listed in the Product table?
value.sql_query: SELECT COUNT(*) AS TotalProducts FROM SalesLT.Product;

value.question: What is the average weight of products in the Product table?
value.sql_query: SELECT AVG(Weight) AS AverageWeight FROM SalesLT.Product;

value.question: List the details of orders placed in the last 30 days.
value.sql_query: SELECT * FROM SalesLT.SalesOrderHeader WHERE OrderDate >= DATEADD(day, -30, GETDATE());

value.question: What are the details of products that cost more than $1000?
value.sql_query: SELECT ProductID, Name, ListPrice FROM SalesLT.Product WHERE ListPrice > 1000;

value.question: List the names of customers who have not placed any orders.
value.sql_query: SELECT c.FirstName, c.LastName FROM SalesLT.Customer c LEFT JOIN SalesLT.SalesOrderHeader soh ON c.CustomerID = soh.CustomerID WHERE soh.CustomerID IS NULL;

value.question: How many unique product categories are there?
value.sql_query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Name) AS UniqueCategories FROM SalesLT.ProductCategory;

value.question: What is the highest unit price of any product sold?
value.sql_query: SELECT MAX(UnitPrice) AS HighestUnitPrice FROM SalesLT.SalesOrderDetail;

value.question: List the names and phone numbers of all customers who have a suffix.
value.sql_query: SELECT FirstName, LastName, Phone FROM SalesLT.Customer WHERE Suffix IS NOT NULL;

value.question: What are the details of the product with the lowest list price?
value.sql_query: SELECT TOP 1 ProductID, Name, ListPrice FROM SalesLT.Product ORDER BY ListPrice ASC;
